How to update:
-Place your miniatures on this tray and press "Update UI".
-Only works for miniatures with extended UI (KT UI Extender).

Instructions:
-To start, select "Movement" in the context menu of each miniature.
-Press from 1 to 6 to select the max distance for each step.
-Press 9 to add a new step.
-Press 8 to delete the last step.
-Press 0 to move the miniature to the last step.
